review_body: Though it's not an official app, but does everything that bing maps actually can do.
Don't touch it!  It's not Bing Maps because it's not made by Microsoft Corporation.

I was surprised at first to see this app was free. Liking Bing as I do, I thought I'd give this a try. It does everything I would expect from a map.

I tapped on my state, then zoomed right in to my address. This is pretty recent, as there is a roundabout shown that has been just recent completed.

I would recommend this to anyone.
